NEWEST UPDATE FEATURES: As requested by many users we have added the option to DELETE your videos individually instead of starting over from the start ! Another popular request was the option to ADD MUSIC AUDIO to your video clips so we have also added this ! We have fixed the bugs from the last update that wouldn t let you save video load the app properly. We are trying to improve the APP with all features users have suggested so keep suggesting and we will try get it done : Insta Video Merge: Trim and merge your videos into the one INSTAGRAM FACEBOOK VINE SOCIAL MEDIA clip. Super simple and easy to use Simply select your videos Trim to desired length Merge together and post to Instagram Social Media ! And best of all it s completely FREE !! Features: Trim videos Merge videos Add music audio to your videos Record your own videos Upload to Instagram Upload to Facebook Upload to Vine Save to camera roll for use anywhere !!
